Cell["\<\
We have obtained,  
Provisional p - sig (E1) = (m,2m,3m)
Let be m=n+k (k=0,1,2,3), then
         p-sig(E1)=(k+4 n,2 k+8 n,3 k+12 n)
    Iso=p^n ---> p-minimal
        p-sig(E1)=(k,2 k+2 n,3 k)\[LineSeparator]    k = 0 -- -> (0, 2n, 0) \
-- n no 0 -> (0, \[GreaterEqual] 0, 0)-- > I0
   k = 1 -- -> (1,2+2n,3)--> (1, \[GreaterEqual] 2, 3)-- > III
    k = 2-- -> (2 ,4+2n, 6) -> (2 ,\[GreaterEqual] 4 , 6)-- > I0^*
    k = 3 -- -> (3, 6+2n, 9)-- > (3, \[GreaterEqual] 6, 9)-- > III^*\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8881433308879223`*^9, 3.888143374571212*^9}, {
   3.888143571828759*^9, 3.8881436034019003`*^9}, {3.8881436884055853`*^9, 
   3.8881438177795277`*^9}, 3.888144227041486*^9, {3.8881449924051027`*^9, 
