 ")=4n+k>0   :  === (u=p^n)  ===>    p-sig(E13)=(k,2 k+2 n,3 k)\
\[LineSeparator]     k = 0 -- -> (0, 2n, 0) -- n no 0 -> (0, \[GreaterEqual] \
0, 0)-- > I0\n   k = 1 -- -> (1,2+2n,3)--> (1, \[GreaterEqual] 2, 3)-- > III\n\
    k = 2-- -> (2 ,4+2n, 6) -> (2 ,\[GreaterEqual] 4 , 6)-- > I0^*\n    k = 3 \
-- -> (3, 6+2n, 9)-- > (3, \[GreaterEqual] 6, 9)-- > III^*"
}], "Subsubsection",
