Cell["\<\
We have obtained,  TODO TODOTODOTODOTODO
Provisional p - sig (E1) = (m,m,2m)
Let be m=6n+k (k=0,1,2,3,4,5), then
         p-sig(E1)=(6n+k,6n+k,2k+12n)
    Iso=p^n --\[Rule] p-minimal 
        p-sig(E1)=(2n+k,k,2k)\[LineSeparator]    k = 0 -- -> (2 n, 0, 0) -- n \
no 0 -> (>= 2, 0, 0)-- > I_0
   k = 1 -- -> (2 n + 1, 1, 2)--> (>= 1, 1, 2)-- > II
    k = 2-- -> (2 n + 2, 2, 4) -> (>= 2, 2, 4)-- > IV
    k = 3 -- -> (2 n + 3, 3, 6)-- > (>= 3, 3, 6)-- > I0^*
    k = 4 -- -> (2 n + 4, 4, 8)-- > (>= 4, 4, 8)-- > IV^*
    k = 5 -- -> (2 n + 5, 5, 10) --> (>= 5, 5, 10) -- > II^*
\
\>", "Text",
